      "value": "<p><b>Source</b> <em>Adventurer's Armory 2 pg. 9</em>, <em>Gnomes of Golarion pg. 22</em></p><h3><span title=\"PFS Legal\">[PFS]</span> Statistics</h3><p><b>Cost</b> 30 gp <b>Weight</b> 12 lbs.</p><p><b>Damage</b> 1d8 (small), 1d10 (medium); <b>Critical</b> x3; <b>Range</b> -; <b>Type</b> S; <b>Special</b> reach, see text</p><p><b>Category</b> Two-Handed; <b>Proficiency</b> Exotic</p><p><b>Weapon Groups</b> Polearms</p><h3>Description</h3><p>The blade of this glaive is serrated and mounted on an axle, around which a heavy cord is wrapped. When the cord is pulled as a move action, the blade spins rapidly for a number of rounds equal to your Strength bonus. While the blade is spinning, you gain a +2 bonus on damage rolls with the weapon. When the blade is not spinning, treat this weapon as a glaive.</p>"
